data.title: Chronic Fatigue Syndrome
data.meta_description: WaPo_3005 - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document discusses the end of the COVID-19 public health emergency in the United States and how that has negatively impacted many patients suffering from long COVID. It talks about how long COVID patients fear being abandoned as clinics close and research into long COVID may stop. The summary also mentions how the end of the public health emergency represented a pivotal moment for long COVID patients.
